title: 'Squid Game' Cast Answer The Most Googled Squid Game Questions
text: Squid Game stars Lee Byung-hun, Lee Jung-jae, Lee Seo-hwan, Jo Yu-ri, Yim Si-wan, Kang Ae-sim, and Yang Dong-geun answer the most searched for questions about the internationally-acclaimed show. Season 2 of Squid Game releases December 26 on Netflix Director: Jackie Phillips Director of Photography: AJ Young Editor: J.Y. Chun; Jaeho Shin Talent: Lee Byung-hun; Lee Jung-jae; Lee Seo-hwan; Jo Yu-ri; Yim Si-wan; Kang Ae-sim; Yang Dong-geun Creative Producer: Justin Wolfson Line Producer: Joseph Buscemi Associate Producer: Paul Gulyas Production Manager: Peter Brunette Talent Booker: Mica Medoff Camera Operator: Shay Eberle-Gunst; Marques Smith Gaffer: Dominik Czaczyk Sound Mixer: Paul Cornett; Gloria "Glo" Hernandez Production Assistant: Fernando Barajas; Spencer Mathesen Translator: Haley Jung; Minji Son Post Production Supervisor: Christian Olguin Post Production Coordinator: Ian Bryant Supervising Editor: Doug Larsen Additional Editor: Jason Malizia Assistant Editor: Fynn Lithgow
